Dialogue: 2,0:02:59.95,0:03:02.00,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我看见他从她家出来
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.95,0:03:02.00,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I saw him coming out of her house.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:02.16,0:03:03.25,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你看到什么了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.16,0:03:03.25,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,What did you see?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:03.41,0:03:06.83,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,他骑上马消失了 看起来像是喝多了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.41,0:03:06.83,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,He mounted his horse and disappeared. He was drunk.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:07.41,0:03:10.29,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你怎么能确定是他呢 那个巷子很黑
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.41,0:03:10.29,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,How could you even be sure it was him? That alley's very dark.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:10.54,0:03:11.75,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,他一瘸一拐的
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.54,0:03:11.75,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,He was limping.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:13.04,0:03:15.16,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,他不是镇上唯一跛行的人
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.04,0:03:15.16,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,He's not the only man in town who limps.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:15.29,0:03:17.00,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,他是我所知道的唯一的左撇子
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.29,0:03:17.00,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,He is the only lefty I know of.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:17.00,0:03:18.75,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,他的左腿一瘸一拐
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.00,0:03:18.75,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,He was limping on his left leg.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:19.29,0:03:20.87,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你跟其他人说过吗
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.29,0:03:20.87,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Have you told anyone?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:20.87,0:03:23.12,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,大家都是这样认为的 治安官
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.87,0:03:23.12,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Everyone is already thinking it, sheriff.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:23.54,0:03:24.95,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你还是闭嘴吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.54,0:03:24.95,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Just keep your mouth shut.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:25.45,0:03:26.45,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.45,0:03:26.45,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:44.95,0:03:46.79,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,Silva先生本尊
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.95,0:03:46.79,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Mr Silva in person!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:49.70,0:03:51.08,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你好吗 Jake
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.70,0:03:51.08,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,How are you, Jake?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:51.25,0:03:52.45,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我很好
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.25,0:03:52.45,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I'm good.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:52.91,0:03:54.33,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,什么风把你吹来了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.91,0:03:54.33,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,What brings you to town?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:54.45,0:03:57.70,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,哦 我的背痛得要命 听说你镇上有一位良医
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.45,0:03:57.70,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Oh, my back is killing me and I hear you have a good doctor in town.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:57.87,0:03:59.45,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你看起来还好啊
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.87,0:03:59.45,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,But you look well.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:00.12,0:04:01.75,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,不 你才是
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.12,0:04:01.75,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,No, it's you...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:02.33,0:04:03.62,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,这身行头不错啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.33,0:04:03.62,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,who look impressive...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:03.79,0:04:05.58,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,像个治安官的样子
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.79,0:04:05.58,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,dressed as a Sheriff!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:05.58,0:04:07.37,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我不是打扮得像
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.58,0:04:07.37,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I'm not just dressed as one.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:07.54,0:04:08.66,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我就是
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.54,0:04:08.66,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I am one.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:08.91,0:04:10.16,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,嗯 很适合你
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.91,0:04:10.16,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Well, it suits you.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:16.20,0:04:17.75,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,- 我饿了  - 嗯嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.20,0:04:17.75,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,- I was hungry. - Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:17.75,0:04:19.04,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,这是你做的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.75,0:04:19.04,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,You made this?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:19.16,0:04:20.20,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.16,0:04:20.20,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:20.58,0:04:22.00,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我不知道你还会做饭
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.58,0:04:22.00,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I didn't know you could cook.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:23.12,0:04:26.16,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你还没有那么了解我 Silva
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.12,0:04:26.16,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,There's a great many things you don't know about me, Silva.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:26.91,0:04:28.29,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.91,0:04:28.29,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:28.54,0:04:30.12,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,25年可不是开玩笑的
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.54,0:04:30.12,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,25 years is a very long time.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:32.08,0:04:33.50,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,为了我们的重逢
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.08,0:04:33.50,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,To our reunion.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:34.87,0:04:35.87,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,不管为了什么
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.87,0:04:35.87,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,To whatever you like.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:39.75,0:04:41.58,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,每当我喝红酒时
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.75,0:04:41.58,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Every time I drink wine,
Dialogue: 2,0:04:42.16,0:04:43.91,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,就会想起我们在墨西哥
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.16,0:04:43.91,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I remember when we were in Mexico
Dialogue: 2,0:04:43.91,0:04:45.83,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,和那几个站街女潜入酒窖的场景
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.91,0:04:45.83,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,and we went down into the cellar with some whores.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:45.83,0:04:47.50,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我们年少轻狂
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.83,0:04:47.50,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,We were very young and very crazy.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:48.12,0:04:49.58,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,真是一群乌合之众啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.12,0:04:49.58,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,What a bunch of misfits!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:50.91,0:04:52.91,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,全员恶人
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.91,0:04:52.91,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,The worst from every county.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:53.20,0:04:54.62,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,也许
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.20,0:04:54.62,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:54.62,0:04:56.58,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我们应该是唯一幸存下来的人
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.62,0:04:56.58,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I think we're the only ones who've survived.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:57.95,0:04:58.95,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,干杯吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.95,0:04:58.95,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Let's drink to that!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:03.45,0:05:04.91,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,别这样看着我
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.45,0:05:04.91,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Don't look at me like that.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:05.16,0:05:06.75,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你想让我怎样看你
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.16,0:05:06.75,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,How do you want me to look at you?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:09.08,0:05:11.20,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,那段不堪回首的过往持续了多久
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.08,0:05:11.20,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,How long did that madness last?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:11.20,0:05:12.25,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,两个月
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.20,0:05:12.25,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Two months.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:15.04,0:05:16.41,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,这并不是什么不堪回首
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.04,0:05:16.41,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,And it wasn't madness.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:17.29,0:05:18.54,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我喝得烂醉
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.29,0:05:18.54,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,When I drink,
Dialogue: 2,0:05:19.91,0:05:22.54,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,但这60天的每一天我都记忆犹新
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.91,0:05:22.54,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I remember every single one of those sixty days...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:23.45,0:05:24.95,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你喝多了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.45,0:05:24.95,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I think you drink too much.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:25.79,0:05:28.37,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我早已经...释然了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.79,0:05:28.37,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I myself have... given it up.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:30.37,0:05:32.58,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,虽然 我现在还是会胡思乱想
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.37,0:05:32.58,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Of course, now I'm contradicting myself.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:32.58,0:05:34.23,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,那么就你敬你的胡思乱想
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.58,0:05:34.23,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,To your contradictions then.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:43.79,0:06:44.79,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,Jake
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.79,0:06:44.79,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Jake?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:16.70,0:07:17.41,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,Jake
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.70,0:07:17.41,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Jake?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:22.16,0:07:23.87,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你骗了我 Silva
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.16,0:07:23.87,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I think you lied to me, Silva.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:23.87,0:07:26.08,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你一直都藏在浴缸里吗
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.87,0:07:26.08,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Were you hiding in the bathtub?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:26.29,0:07:27.58,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我没有藏
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.29,0:07:27.58,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I wasn't hiding.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:27.83,0:07:29.37,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你也可以来洗嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.83,0:07:29.37,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,You could use a bath yourself.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:30.33,0:07:32.66,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你是在邀请我跟你共浴吗
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.33,0:07:32.66,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Are you inviting me to take a bath together?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:32.95,0:07:33.95,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.95,0:07:33.95,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:36.75,0:07:37.75,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,不用你
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.75,0:07:37.75,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:38.04,0:07:39.62,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我自己会擦干
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.04,0:07:39.62,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I know how to dry myself.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:42.45,0:07:43.62,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你还是穿条裤子吧
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.45,0:07:43.62,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,You should get dressed.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:44.62,0:07:46.45,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我把内裤放哪儿了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.62,0:07:46.45,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Where did I put my underpants?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:46.83,0:07:48.04,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,穿我的吧
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.83,0:07:48.04,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Take a pair of mine.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:48.70,0:07:50.23,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,在右边的抽屉里
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.70,0:07:50.23,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,They're in the drawer on the right.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:01.75,0:08:03.37,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你还是骗了我 Silva
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.75,0:08:03.37,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,And you did lie to me, Silva.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:05.00,0:08:06.91,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你的背没毛病
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.00,0:08:06.91,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,You don't have a bad back.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:06.91,0:08:07.91,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你什​​么意思
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.91,0:08:07.91,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:09.50,0:08:11.00,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你也不需要看医生
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.50,0:08:11.00,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,And you don't need a doctor.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:12.33,0:08:16.44,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我想在我还能动弹的时候 再和你喝几杯
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.33,0:08:16.44,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I wanted to have a couple of drinks with you again, while I can still move. 
Dialogue: 2,0:08:17.45,0:08:20.04,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,不管你信不信
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.45,0:08:20.04,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,And... believe it or not,
Dialogue: 2,0:08:20.79,0:08:22.91,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,长期骑马 真的很伤背
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.79,0:08:22.91,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,working with horses destroys your back.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:23.50,0:08:24.95,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你随意
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.50,0:08:24.95,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,No one would ever know.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:26.37,0:08:27.90,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,不过今早却不疼了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.37,0:08:27.90,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Nothing hurts this morning.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:29.91,0:08:31.41,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你治好了我的旧疾
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.91,0:08:31.41,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,You cured all my ailments.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:35.04,0:08:37.45,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,这种舒适感真是久违了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.04,0:08:37.45,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I haven't felt this good in such a long time.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:38.54,0:08:39.70,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你今天要做什么
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.54,0:08:39.70,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,What are you doing today?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:40.41,0:08:42.20,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我们可以去热山河
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.41,0:08:42.20,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,We could go to Hot Mountain river.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:42.20,0:08:43.66,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,今天我要工作
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.20,0:08:43.66,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I've got work today.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:44.20,0:08:45.50,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,工作可以等等
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.20,0:08:45.50,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Work can wait.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:47.75,0:08:51.37,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,并不是每天都会有人穿越沙漠来看你
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.75,0:08:51.37,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,It's not every day someone crosses the desert to come see you.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:53.50,0:08:56.87,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我们已经庆祝过了 我还有事
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.50,0:08:56.87,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,We've celebrated enough. I've got things to do.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:56.87,0:08:57.79,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,需要我帮忙吗
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.87,0:08:57.79,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Can I help?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:58.95,0:08:59.62,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,可能吧
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.95,0:08:59.62,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:01.66,0:09:02.33,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.66,0:09:02.33,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:05.58,0:09:06.83,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,三天前
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.58,0:09:06.83,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Three days ago
Dialogue: 2,0:09:07.95,0:09:10.41,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,一个女人在镇上被杀害了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.95,0:09:10.41,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,a woman was found killed in town.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:10.99,0:09:13.45,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我必须找到凶手并将他绳之以法
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.99,0:09:13.45,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I've got to find the man who did it and bring him to justice.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:13.45,0:09:17.16,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你就不能找别人帮你做吗 你是治安官...
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.45,0:09:17.16,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Can't you find someone else to do it for you? You are the Sheriff...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:18.16,0:09:19.75,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,这关乎荣誉
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.16,0:09:19.75,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,It's a question of honour.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:20.54,0:09:23.12,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,被杀的女人是我弟媳
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.54,0:09:23.12,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,The woman killed is my brother's wife.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:23.83,0:09:25.83,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我代表的是法律 
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.83,0:09:25.83,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,And I'm the law around here, remember?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:27.00,0:09:28.70,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,真是造物弄人啊
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.00,0:09:28.70,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Ours is a strange fate.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:29.50,0:09:30.50,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.50,0:09:30.50,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:32.12,0:09:36.08,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我们能再续前缘竟然要感谢你弟媳的离世
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.12,0:09:36.08,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Your brother's wife had to die for us to find each other in the same bed again.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:36.08,0:09:38.18,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,- 昨晚... - 昨晚我们喝多了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.08,0:09:38.18,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,- Last night... - Last night we drank too much.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:38.18,0:09:40.04,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我们喝酒是久别重逢之喜
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.18,0:09:40.04,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,We drank because we were happy to be together.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:40.04,0:09:43.50,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,那又怎样 你儿子依然要为他的罪行付出代价
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.04,0:09:43.50,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,That's not gonna spare your son from paying for what he did!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:43.50,0:09:44.26,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,不是他做的
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.50,0:09:44.26,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,He didn't do it!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:44.26,0:09:46.38,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,他们是恋人 他却虐待她
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.26,0:09:46.38,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,They were lovers, he mistreated her.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:47.66,0:09:49.95,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,他一定告诉过你 他时常来这里吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.66,0:09:49.95,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,He must have told you he came here from time to time?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:49.95,0:09:51.91,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,不 我会问他关于你的事
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.95,0:09:51.91,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,No, I would've asked him about you.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:53.62,0:09:55.83,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,Jake 别走 我在跟你说话
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.62,0:09:55.83,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Jake, don't walk away, I'm talking to you.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:55.83,0:09:57.62,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我弟弟去世时
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.83,0:09:57.62,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,When my brother died
Dialogue: 2,0:09:57.95,0:10:00.75,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我向他保证我会照顾她
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.95,0:10:00.75,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I promised him that I would look after her.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:01.58,0:10:03.58,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,她不是很好相处 但我还是信守承诺
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.58,0:10:03.58,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,She wasn't an easy woman, but I made a promise.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:03.58,0:10:06.25,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,早在在我父亲临终前
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.58,0:10:06.25,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Before then, on my father's deathbed,
Dialogue: 2,0:10:06.25,0:10:08.58,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我就答应过他 要照顾我的弟弟
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.25,0:10:08.58,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I promised him I'd look after my little brother.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:09.33,0:10:10.79,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我不能让他们任何一个人失望
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.33,0:10:10.79,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I can't fail any of them.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:10.79,0:10:12.30,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我听说你和她有一腿
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.79,0:10:12.30,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I heard you had an affair with her.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:12.30,0:10:13.58,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,那是很久以前的事
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.30,0:10:13.58,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,That was a long time ago.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:13.58,0:10:14.91,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,那时你弟弟尚在人世吗
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.58,0:10:14.91,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Was your brother still alive?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:16.08,0:10:17.00,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,跟这没关
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.08,0:10:17.00,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:19.91,0:10:21.12,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,重要的是...
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.91,0:10:21.12,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,What matters...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:21.12,0:10:23.91,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,有人看到一个左腿跛行的男人
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.12,0:10:23.91,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,is someone saw a man with a limp on his left leg
Dialogue: 2,0:10:23.91,0:10:26.25,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,在她被杀的那天晚上 离开了她的住处
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.91,0:10:26.25,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,leaving her place the night she was killed.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:26.25,0:10:29.45,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,如果你的儿子没有跛腿 他就没有什么可担心的
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.25,0:10:29.45,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Now, if your son didn't have a limp he'd have nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:29.45,0:10:32.79,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我知道你穿越沙漠 来为他保驾护航
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.45,0:10:32.79,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I understand you've crossed the desert to intervene on his behalf.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:32.79,0:10:35.58,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,任何人都可以假装跛腿来陷害他
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.79,0:10:35.58,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Anyone could have pretended to have a limp to frame him.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:35.58,0:10:37.62,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你为什么要到这来 Silva
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.58,0:10:37.62,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Why have you come here, Silva?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:37.62,0:10:38.89,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我来是因为我想见你
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.62,0:10:38.89,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I came because I wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:38.89,0:10:40.78,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我真的很想你
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.89,0:10:40.78,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I've been wanting to see you for a long time...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:40.78,0:10:42.29,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,别扯了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.78,0:10:42.29,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Bullshit!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:43.89,0:10:45.12,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你怎么不早点来
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.89,0:10:45.12,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,You could have come much sooner.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:45.12,0:10:46.70,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我真的有想过 相信我
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.12,0:10:46.70,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I thought about it, believe me.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:47.33,0:10:49.87,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我不敢想象你会如何接纳我
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.33,0:10:49.87,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,But I didn't know what kind of welcome I would get from you.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:50.79,0:10:53.50,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我感觉你是有意在疏远我
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.79,0:10:53.50,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I got the feeling that you put distance between us on purpose.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:54.08,0:10:55.74,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,结束了雇佣兵的生活后
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.08,0:10:55.74,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,After working together as hired guns,
Dialogue: 2,0:10:55.74,0:10:59.06,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我提议我们两个人一起经营牧场 但是你不同意
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.74,0:10:59.06,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I proposed to set up a ranch, the two of us, but you didn't want to!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:59.06,0:11:02.20,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我要回家照看病重的父亲
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.06,0:11:02.20,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I left to be with my father, who was sick!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:02.20,0:11:04.07,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,最后一次尝试做个好儿子
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.20,0:11:04.07,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I decided to be a good son for once.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:04.07,0:11:06.73,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,想成为一个好儿子 也不必要变成一个复仇的法官
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.07,0:11:06.73,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,You don't have to be an avenging judge to be a good son.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:06.73,0:11:10.58,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我想站在法律的一边 我厌倦了雇佣兵的生活
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.73,0:11:10.58,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I wanted to be on the right side of the law. I was sick of being a hired gun.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:11.20,0:11:13.20,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,而且 我并不适合做牧场主
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.20,0:11:13.20,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Besides I'm not cut out to be a rancher.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:13.50,0:11:14.91,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你是最优秀的枪手
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.50,0:11:14.91,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,You were the best gunman.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:15.25,0:11:16.78,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,嗯 这点倒是没变
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.25,0:11:16.78,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Well, that hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:18.58,0:11:20.33,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,百密必有一疏...
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.58,0:11:20.33,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,There was one day you missed...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:21.66,0:11:22.83,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.66,0:11:22.83,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:24.29,0:11:25.04,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.29,0:11:25.04,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:27.04,0:11:28.81,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,常在河边走
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.04,0:11:28.81,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,No matter how good you are with a gun,
Dialogue: 2,0:11:28.81,0:11:30.62,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,哪能不湿鞋
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.81,0:11:30.62,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,there will come a day where you miss the shot.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:31.25,0:11:32.41,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,适用于所有人
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.25,0:11:32.41,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,It happens to all of us.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:33.25,0:11:34.33,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你不记得了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.25,0:11:34.33,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,You don't remember?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:35.83,0:11:37.58,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我不知道你在说什么
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.83,0:11:37.58,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:39.29,0:11:41.95,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你在维护法律这方面 做得很出色
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.29,0:11:41.95,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I will say you've done very well on this side of the law.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:41.95,0:11:44.95,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你是全县最受尊敬的治安官
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.95,0:11:44.95,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,You're the most respected sheriff in the county.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:44.95,0:11:48.53,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你清者自清就好了 分手对我们双方都有好处
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.95,0:11:48.53,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,You've done well for yourself. The split's been good for both of us.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:51.29,0:11:54.09,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,但我知道有一天我会穿越沙漠再次与你相遇
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.29,0:11:54.09,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,But I knew that one day I would cross the desert to come and see you again.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:54.09,0:11:55.58,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,别扯这些了 Silva
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.09,0:11:55.58,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Don't go down that path, Silva.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:55.58,0:11:58.08,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我真的很怀念在墨西哥的那2个月 难道你不怀念吗
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.58,0:11:58.08,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I miss those two months in Mexico. Don't you?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:58.08,0:12:00.62,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,那已经是很久以前的事了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.08,0:12:00.62,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,That was a long time ago.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:00.62,0:12:03.41,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我的生活在这边 而你的生活在沙漠的另一边
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.62,0:12:03.41,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,My life is here now and yours is on the other side of the desert.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:03.41,0:12:05.30,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我知道你还留着我的红围巾
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.41,0:12:05.30,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I like that you've kept my red scarf.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:06.58,0:12:08.45,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,如果不是为了救你儿子
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.58,0:12:08.45,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,If not to save your boy,
Dialogue: 2,0:12:08.45,0:12:10.62,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你为什么在这个时间来
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.45,0:12:10.62,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,why have you come here precisely now?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:10.62,0:12:11.87,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我想见你
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.62,0:12:11.87,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I wanted to see you,
Dialogue: 2,0:12:11.87,0:12:13.95,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,- 我已经告诉过你了...  - 我不相信你
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.87,0:12:13.95,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,- I've told you... - I don't believe you!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:14.87,0:12:17.50,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,25年了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.87,0:12:17.50,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,You had 25 years for that.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:17.79,0:12:20.79,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,直到最后一刻我才知道 我是多么想见到你
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.79,0:12:20.79,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I spent the last hours showing you how much I wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:23.44,0:12:25.12,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你爱你弟媳胜过爱我吗
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.44,0:12:25.12,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Did you love your sister-in-law more than you loved me?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:25.12,0:12:27.31,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我答应过我弟弟的 我说过
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.12,0:12:27.31,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I promised my brother, I told you!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:28.16,0:12:30.75,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,别再说这种话了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.16,0:12:30.75,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Just stop talking like that!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:30.75,0:12:31.94,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,这里只有我们两个
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.75,0:12:31.94,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,We are alone.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:32.48,0:12:35.16,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,25年前你就犯了一个错误
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.48,0:12:35.16,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,You made a mistake 25 years ago,
Dialogue: 2,0:12:35.16,0:12:38.12,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,认为我们可以一起创业生活
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.16,0:12:38.12,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,thinking we could start a business together.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:38.12,0:12:40.37,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,而你现在又犯了一个错误
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.12,0:12:40.37,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,And you're making a mistake right now.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:40.37,0:12:42.42,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,穿好衣服就赶快上路吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.37,0:12:42.42,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Just finish getting dressed and go on your way!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:42.42,0:12:43.87,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我的路就是你...
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.42,0:12:43.87,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,My way is yours...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:45.22,0:12:47.37,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我开始担心你说的可能是对的
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.22,0:12:47.37,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I'm starting to worry you might be right about that.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:48.79,0:12:51.37,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,为什么你这么肯定是我儿子干的
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.79,0:12:51.37,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Why are you so sure it was my son?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:51.37,0:12:54.06,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,有人看到他们在一起
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.37,0:12:54.06,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,People saw them together.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:54.06,0:12:56.53,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,他们有过争吵
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.06,0:12:56.53,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,They had a violent relationship.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:58.55,0:13:00.36,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,Silva 你儿子是个危险人物
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.55,0:13:00.36,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Silva, your son is dangerous.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:01.33,0:13:02.58,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我跟他说过
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.33,0:13:02.58,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I told him...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:03.20,0:13:06.41,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我告诉他永远不要再踏足这里
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.20,0:13:06.41,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I told him to never set foot here, in Bitter Creek, again
Dialogue: 2,0:13:06.41,0:13:08.87,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你看...他有多么听我的话
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.41,0:13:08.87,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,and you see... you see how much he listened to me.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:08.87,0:13:13.12,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我会让他去墨西哥 或者一个不会打扰你我的地方
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.87,0:13:13.12,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I'll make him to go to Mexico or any place where he won't bother you or me.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:13.12,0:13:15.20,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,外面的世界很大
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.12,0:13:15.20,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,It's a big world out there.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:15.66,0:13:17.50,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我要带他去受审
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.66,0:13:17.50,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I'm gonna bring him into trial,
Dialogue: 2,0:13:17.95,0:13:21.47,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,如果他被判无罪 我确保他不会有事
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.95,0:13:21.47,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,if he's found innocent, I will make sure nothing happens to him.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:21.47,0:13:23.87,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,但你不必去搜捕他 就...
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.47,0:13:23.87,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,But you don't need to be the one looking for him! Just...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:25.33,0:13:26.20,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我们休战
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.33,0:13:26.20,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Give me a truce.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:27.67,0:13:28.58,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,休战
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.67,0:13:28.58,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,A truce!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:30.29,0:13:31.62,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.29,0:13:31.62,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:34.80,0:13:36.34,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你没有心 Jake
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.80,0:13:36.34,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,You have no heart, Jake.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:38.45,0:13:39.50,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你从来没有过
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.45,0:13:39.50,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,You never did.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:42.37,0:13:44.37,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你只喜欢做是吧
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.37,0:13:44.37,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,You just like to fuck, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:45.14,0:13:47.12,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你从来没有爱过我 你这辈子从来没有爱过任何人
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.14,0:13:47.12,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,You never loved me, you've never loved anyone in your life!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:47.12,0:13:48.16,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你再说一句
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.12,0:13:48.16,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:51.21,0:13:52.08,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你要开枪打我吗
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.21,0:13:52.08,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,You gonna shoot me?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:52.70,0:13:53.95,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,够了 Silva
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.70,0:13:53.95,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Enough, Silva!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:53.95,0:13:56.16,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你要趁我半裸的时候杀了我吗
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.95,0:13:56.16,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,You gonna to kill me while I'm half undressed?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:56.78,0:13:58.16,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你打算作何解释
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.78,0:13:58.16,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,How will you explain that?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:58.16,0:14:01.20,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,一具尸体躺在你的床上 满身是精华液的味道
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.16,0:14:01.20,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,A dead man in your bed still smelling of cum!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:02.91,0:14:04.66,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,滚出去
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.91,0:14:04.66,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Get the fuck out of my house.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:42.54,0:14:43.20,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.54,0:14:43.20,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:43.75,0:14:44.79,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,早上好治安官
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.75,0:14:44.79,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Good morning Sheriff
Dialogue: 2,0:14:59.87,0:15:00.75,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,把这个锁好
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.87,0:15:00.75,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Lock this up.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:01.12,0:15:03.20,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,在我回来之前你负责管理
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.12,0:15:03.20,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,You're in charge of the office till I get back.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:03.79,0:15:05.04,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你什么时候回来
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.79,0:15:05.04,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,When are you gonna be back?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:06.37,0:15:07.20,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.37,0:15:07.20,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:01.83,0:16:03.79,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,这有好多酒啊
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.83,0:16:03.79,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,There is plenty of wine!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:03.79,0:16:06.79,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,- 但是我们怎么喝得完呢 Silva  - 交给我们吧
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.79,0:16:06.79,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,{\i1}- But how do we drink it, Silva? - Leave it to us... ¿Sí?{\i}
Dialogue: 2,0:16:07.41,0:16:09.25,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,那就练习射击怎么样 Silva
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.41,0:16:09.25,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Let's do some target shooting, Silva.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:09.66,0:16:11.50,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,看看你能不能打到酒袋
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.66,0:16:11.50,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Let's see if you can hit the wineskin.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:11.75,0:16:12.62,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.75,0:16:12.62,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:13.12,0:16:15.25,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,女士们 请靠边站
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.12,0:16:15.25,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Ladies, please, step aside.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:15.25,0:16:16.25,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.25,0:16:16.25,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:16.50,0:16:17.58,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,看看吧
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.50,0:16:17.58,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:21.62,0:16:22.62,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你准备好了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.62,0:16:22.62,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:22.62,0:16:23.70,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,时刻准备
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.62,0:16:23.70,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Always.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:25.16,0:16:27.20,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,一二...
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.16,0:16:27.20,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,One... Two...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:51.41,0:16:53.04,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我不能再喝了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.41,0:16:53.04,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I can't drink anymore.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:53.62,0:16:54.83,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,看他们
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.62,0:16:54.83,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Look at them!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:54.83,0:16:56.75,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,他们比我们差太多了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.83,0:16:56.75,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,They are so much worse than us.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:56.75,0:16:59.04,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我们走吧 这里没我们的事了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.75,0:16:59.04,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Let's go. We have nothing to do here.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:59.95,0:17:01.45,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我们去呼吸一下新鲜空气吧 
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.95,0:17:01.45,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Let's grab some fresh air.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:01.45,0:17:03.91,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,派对从现在开始
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.45,0:17:03.91,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,It's now the party really begins!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:28.58,0:19:29.25,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,Joe
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.58,0:19:29.25,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Joe!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:35.45,0:19:36.25,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,Joe
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.45,0:19:36.25,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Joe?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:38.29,0:19:39.62,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,起来 穿好衣服赶快离开
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.29,0:19:39.62,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Come on, get dressed and leave.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:40.25,0:19:41.75,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,- 怎么了  - 穿衣服
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.25,0:19:41.75,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,- What's wrong? - Get dressed!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:42.91,0:19:45.45,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,自从我离开苦溪 Jake就一直尾随着我
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.91,0:19:45.45,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Jake has been on my tail since I left Bitter Creek.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:45.45,0:19:47.20,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,- 你不能说服他吗  - 不能
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.45,0:19:47.20,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,- Couldn't you convince him? - No!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:48.29,0:19:49.79,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,然后骑马...
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.29,0:19:49.79,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,And you take a horse...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:49.79,0:19:51.50,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,走得越远越好
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.79,0:19:51.50,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,and you get as far away as you can.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:51.86,0:19:53.91,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,无论你在哪里 Jake都会找到你
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.86,0:19:53.91,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Even though no matter where you are, Jake will find you.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:54.20,0:19:55.87,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,她是个站街女 父亲
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.20,0:19:55.87,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,She was a whore, Father.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:57.29,0:19:59.04,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,迟早她也会落得这样的下场
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.29,0:19:59.04,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Sooner or later, she'd have end up like that.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:00.22,0:20:01.37,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你们不过臭味相投
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.22,0:20:01.37,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,You were two of a kind!
Dialogue: 2,0:20:02.21,0:20:04.84,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,在我亲手绞死你之前 赶快离开这里
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.21,0:20:04.84,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Now get out of here before I hang you myself.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:05.79,0:20:06.37,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.79,0:20:06.37,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:16.97,0:20:18.41,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,去阿瓜杜尔塞
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.97,0:20:18.41,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Go to Aguadulce.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:19.12,0:20:21.04,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,老Raúl有一个铁匠铺 他会让你去那里
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.12,0:20:21.04,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Old Raúl has a smithy and he will let you in.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:21.04,0:20:22.66,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,这些应该能够买通他了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.04,0:20:22.66,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,This should be enough to buy his silence.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:24.50,0:20:27.08,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,—这一个月都不够  - 那你就得工作了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.50,0:20:27.08,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,- This is not enough for even a month! - Then you will have to work.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:27.83,0:20:29.54,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,Raúl会给你找点事做
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.83,0:20:29.54,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Raúl will find you something to do.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:36.71,0:20:37.58,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你要去哪里
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.71,0:20:37.58,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 2,0:20:37.58,0:20:39.17,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,去牵马 我得上马鞍
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.58,0:20:39.17,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,To get my fucking horse! I've to saddle him up!
Dialogue: 2,0:20:39.17,0:20:40.95,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,没时间了 骑我的
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.17,0:20:40.95,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,There's no time for that! Take mine.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:41.51,0:20:43.87,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,别想再回到这里了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.51,0:20:43.87,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,And don't even think about crossing the border back here again.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:43.87,0:20:45.25,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,哦 你不用别担心
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.87,0:20:45.25,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Oh, don't you worry.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:45.58,0:20:48.25,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我可不想烂在这个鬼牧场
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.58,0:20:48.25,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I wasn't planning on rotting on this godforsaken ranch!
Dialogue: 2,0:20:48.62,0:20:49.71,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你哪儿也不能去  Joe
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.62,0:20:49.71,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,You're not going anywhere, Joe.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:49.71,0:20:51.20,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,把枪放下 放下
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.71,0:20:51.20,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Put the gun down! Put it down!
Dialogue: 2,0:20:51.20,0:20:52.08,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.20,0:20:52.08,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Right now.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:52.33,0:20:53.58,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,把枪放下 Joe
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.33,0:20:53.58,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Put it down, Joe!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:02.36,0:21:04.25,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,不要背对我... Silva
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.36,0:21:04.25,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Don't turn your back on me... Silva!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:05.12,0:21:06.63,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我是为了你儿子才来的
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.12,0:21:06.63,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I'm only here for your son!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:45.54,0:21:46.83,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,住手 Joe
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.54,0:21:46.83,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Enough, Joe!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:46.83,0:21:47.87,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.83,0:21:47.87,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:48.41,0:21:49.50,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.41,0:21:49.50,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:52.91,0:21:53.95,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,Jake 收起你的枪
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.91,0:21:53.95,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Holster your gun, Jake.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:56.95,0:21:58.33,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,不 住手
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.95,0:21:58.33,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,No! Stop!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:58.33,0:21:59.58,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,Joe 住手
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.33,0:21:59.58,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Joe, stop!
Dialogue: 2,0:22:03.20,0:22:04.25,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,别动...
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.20,0:22:04.25,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Don't move...
Dialogue: 2,0:22:05.08,0:22:07.08,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,不然我会杀了你
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.08,0:22:07.08,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,or I swear I will kill you!
Dialogue: 2,0:22:07.08,0:22:08.66,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,把枪放下 Joe
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.08,0:22:08.66,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Put that gun down, Joe.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:08.66,0:22:09.95,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你闭嘴 Jake
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.66,0:22:09.95,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,No shit, Jake!
Dialogue: 2,0:22:11.29,0:22:14.16,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,骑上马 离开这里
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.29,0:22:14.16,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Now get on the horse and get the fuck out of here!
Dialogue: 2,0:23:41.08,0:23:43.58,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,这一枪直击腰部
Dialogue: 1,0:23:41.08,0:23:43.58,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,It was a clean shot, straight through the waist.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:52.91,0:23:54.70,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,忍一下
Dialogue: 1,0:23:52.91,0:23:54.70,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Okay, okay...
Dialogue: 2,0:23:57.25,0:23:58.62,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你会没事的
Dialogue: 1,0:23:57.25,0:23:58.62,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,You're going to be alright.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:00.45,0:24:02.33,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你去鼠吧 你个王八蛋
Dialogue: 1,0:24:00.45,0:24:02.33,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Rot in hell, you son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 2,0:24:04.58,0:24:05.91,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,压好
Dialogue: 1,0:24:04.58,0:24:05.91,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Keep pressure on it!
Dialogue: 2,0:25:29.58,0:25:32.16,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,所以你现在想清楚了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:25:29.58,0:25:32.16,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,So you think you got it all figured out.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:33.37,0:25:35.66,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,有些事永远无法算计清楚 Jake
Dialogue: 1,0:25:33.37,0:25:35.66,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,These things cannot be calculated, Jake.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:37.87,0:25:40.33,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,这是命运 我们无法逃避
Dialogue: 1,0:25:37.87,0:25:40.33,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,It is destiny and we cannot run away from it.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:41.87,0:25:43.41,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,什么命运
Dialogue: 1,0:25:41.87,0:25:43.41,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,What destiny?
Dialogue: 2,0:25:43.75,0:25:44.75,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我们的
Dialogue: 1,0:25:43.75,0:25:44.75,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Ours.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:47.33,0:25:50.33,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,既然你为了搜捕我的儿子 去跟踪我 
Dialogue: 1,0:25:47.33,0:25:50.33,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,And since you decided to follow me and look for my son,
Dialogue: 2,0:25:51.80,0:25:54.33,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,就说明我们三人的相遇是命中注定的
Dialogue: 1,0:25:51.80,0:25:54.33,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,the three of us were doomed to meet,
Dialogue: 2,0:25:54.33,0:25:56.12,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,-相互对峙  - 你滚
Dialogue: 1,0:25:54.33,0:25:56.12,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,- each of us armed. - Bullshit!
Dialogue: 2,0:25:56.12,0:25:59.00,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你开枪打我 现在你又...想绑架我
Dialogue: 1,0:25:56.12,0:25:59.00,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,You shot me and now you're... trying to kidnap me!
Dialogue: 2,0:25:59.33,0:26:01.12,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我只是想救我的儿子
Dialogue: 1,0:25:59.33,0:26:01.12,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I just wanted to save my son.
Dialogue: 2,0:26:03.33,0:26:04.95,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我很抱歉我不得不向你开枪
Dialogue: 1,0:26:03.33,0:26:04.95,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,And I am sorry I had to shoot you.
Dialogue: 2,0:26:06.00,0:26:08.95,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,现在...你觉得我被你捉住把柄了是吧
Dialogue: 1,0:26:06.00,0:26:08.95,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,And now... you think you've got me in your hands.
Dialogue: 2,0:26:11.50,0:26:13.12,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,放轻松
Dialogue: 1,0:26:11.50,0:26:13.12,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Don't strain yourself.
Dialogue: 2,0:26:13.54,0:26:14.62,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,别说话
Dialogue: 1,0:26:13.54,0:26:14.62,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Don't talk.
Dialogue: 2,0:26:19.37,0:26:21.75,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,只要我能动了 我就会离开这里
Dialogue: 1,0:26:19.37,0:26:21.75,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,As soon as I can ride, I'll leave here
Dialogue: 2,0:26:21.75,0:26:24.04,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我会指控你谋杀未遂
Dialogue: 1,0:26:21.75,0:26:24.04,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,and I'll charge you with attempted murder.
Dialogue: 2,0:26:24.54,0:26:27.41,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,没人能搞清楚为什么我会失手
Dialogue: 1,0:26:24.54,0:26:27.41,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,No one will understand why I missed the shot,
Dialogue: 2,0:26:27.41,0:26:29.83,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,更不用说 为什么我还会给你处理伤口
Dialogue: 1,0:26:27.41,0:26:29.83,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,let alone why I treated your wound afterward.
Dialogue: 2,0:26:33.41,0:26:34.20,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,休息吧
Dialogue: 1,0:26:33.41,0:26:34.20,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Rest.
Dialogue: 2,0:26:37.08,0:26:38.95,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我们有的是时间
Dialogue: 1,0:26:37.08,0:26:38.95,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,There's plenty of time to talk.
Dialogue: 2,0:26:41.54,0:26:45.91,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你这张脸 我看见就想吐
Dialogue: 1,0:26:41.54,0:26:45.91,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,The only reason I would open my mouth is to spit in your face. 
Dialogue: 2,0:26:45.91,0:26:48.41,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,你恨我就恨吧 Jake
Dialogue: 1,0:26:45.91,0:26:48.41,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,You hate me as much as you want, Jake,
Dialogue: 2,0:26:49.95,0:26:52.70,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,即便如此 你的伤口也不会轻易愈合
Dialogue: 1,0:26:49.95,0:26:52.70,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,but it won't help your wound to heal any faster.
Dialogue: 2,0:26:59.08,0:27:00.75,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,很多年前你问过我...
Dialogue: 1,0:26:59.08,0:27:00.75,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,Years ago you asked me...
Dialogue: 2,0:27:02.12,0:27:06.04,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,两个男人一起住在牧场 能做什么
Dialogue: 1,0:27:02.12,0:27:06.04,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,what two men could do living together on a ranch. 
Dialogue: 2,0:27:09.25,0:27:11.16,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,我现在就回答你
Dialogue: 1,0:27:09.25,0:27:11.16,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,I'll answer you now.
Dialogue: 2,0:27:13.58,0:27:15.33,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,他们可以照顾彼此
Dialogue: 1,0:27:13.58,0:27:15.33,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,They can look after one another,
Dialogue: 2,0:27:17.95,0:27:19.45,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,保护彼此
Dialogue: 1,0:27:17.95,0:27:19.45,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,protect each other,
Dialogue: 2,0:27:22.54,0:27:24.70,Pingfang-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,他们可以彼此陪伴
Dialogue: 1,0:27:22.54,0:27:24.70,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,they can keep each other company.
